OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772745123
OL,3,CSafety campaigns rolled out after 15
OL,4,Cdeaths on NI roads so far this year
OL,6,F15 people have died on Northern
OL,7,FIreland's roads already this year.
OL,9,FOn Thursday, two road safety ad
OL,10,Fcampaigns are being rolled out across
OL,11,Fdifferent platforms to illustrate how
OL,12,Fdriver behaviour can cause fatal
OL,13,Faccidents.
OL,15,FHoping to appeal to motorists, to stop
OL,16,Fspeeding and ignore any distractions
OL,17,Fwhile behind the wheel.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
