OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772745123
OL,3,CSafety campaigns rolled out after 15
OL,4,Cdeaths on NI roads so far this year
OL,6,FDebbie Mullan of Road Victim Support
OL,7,FNI-Donegal, spoke to UTV about the
OL,8,Fimportance of the campaign after
OL,9,Flosing her son in a fatal road traffic
OL,10,Fcollision 13 years ago.
OL,12,FDebbie described the videos as "very
OL,13,Femotive".
OL,15,FShe continued: "I hope people take a
OL,16,Fmoment and they sit up and they take
OL,17,Fnotice because while they are hard-
OL,18,Fhitting, they're based on facts.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772745123
OL,3,CSafety campaigns rolled out after 15
OL,4,Cdeaths on NI roads so far this year
OL,6,F"I would hope that people would take
OL,7,Fthe message that they're meant to be,
OL,8,Fas that this can happen to every
OL,9,Fsingle one of us."
OL,11,FThe campaign was launched in Derry, a
OL,12,Fplace still grieving after two of the
OL,13,Fcity's young people died in a car
OL,14,Fcrash near the border with Donegal
OL,15,Flast month.
OL,17,FIn the first two months of 2025, 15
OL,18,Fpeople lost their lives on the roads
OL,19,Fin Northern Ireland. 10 died in the
OL,20,Fsame period last year, and nine in
OL,21,F2024.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772745123
OL,3,CSafety campaigns rolled out after 15
OL,4,Cdeaths on NI roads so far this year
OL,6,FChief Inspector Celeste Simpson, Head
OL,7,Fof Roads Policing, PSNI said: "I think
OL,8,Fevery single person in Northern
OL,9,FIreland can relate to both of those
OL,10,Fvideos.
OL,12,F"We can all see ourselves in those
OL,13,Fvideos - having breakfast, casually
OL,14,Fgoing to work - and again, it's that
OL,15,Fmomentary lapse where we actually...
OL,16,Fthat split second can lead to a
OL,17,Ftragedy.
OL,19,F"So again, our driving behaviours need
OL,20,Fto be our focus whenever we're in the
OL,21,Fcar."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
