OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772745123
OL,3,CSafety campaigns rolled out after 15
OL,4,Cdeaths on NI roads so far this year
OL,6,FTo make the roads safer, the
OL,7,FInfrastructure Minister announced a
OL,8,Frange of additional restrictions for
OL,9,Fnew drivers to be introduced later in
OL,10,Fthe year.
OL,12,FThese new ads are another key part of
OL,13,Fher department's strategy, and it's
OL,14,Fhoped they'll have a lasting impact on
OL,15,Fmotorists.
OL,17,FLiz Kimmins MLA, Infrastructure
OL,18,FMinister said: "We can all remember
OL,19,Fsome of the campaigns that have
OL,20,Fhappened, particularly around TV
OL,21,Fadvertisements.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772745123
OL,3,CSafety campaigns rolled out after 15
OL,4,Cdeaths on NI roads so far this year
OL,6,F"I certainly can remember some of the
OL,7,Fmost hard-hitting ones that happened
OL,8,Fmany years ago, going back even when I
OL,9,Fwas a child myself, and you've seen it
OL,10,Fon the TV.
OL,12,F"They stay with you forever.
OL,14,F"If that helps to change people's
OL,15,Fminds and make people think
OL,16,Fdifferently when they get behind the
OL,17,Fwheel, when they're out on the roads,
OL,18,Feven whether they're out cycling or
OL,19,Fwalking or whatever it may be and then
OL,20,FI can say that that will save lives."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
